<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><?ish ishref="GUID-7F6E847A-CB2F-4EBF-94A0-1A4940D6E7BC" version="2" lang="en-US"?><task xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="GUID-7F6E847A-CB2F-4EBF-94A0-1A4940D6E7BC" xml:lang="en-US" ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3" domains="(topic task)                            (topic hi-d)                            (topic ui-d)                            (topic sw-d)                            (topic indexing-d)                            (topic ut-d)                            a(base ishcondition)                            a(base varid)                            a(base varref)                            a(base cid)                            a(base partslist)                            (topic oce-d)                            (topic sdlVariables-c)                            (topic oceCommonElements-c)                            (topic oceMetaDecl-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c task oceTask-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c hi-d oceHighlight-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c ui-d oceUi-c)                            (topic oceTopic-c sw-d oceSoftware-c)   " class="- topic/topic task/task "><title class="- topic/title ">White and/or dark lines in the first meter after the leading edge</title><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-50B00AD6-0A38-41AB-B3CF-DCE2951AFA8A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "/><table id="GUID-53E5F599-B620-44AD-919D-C7253ABD770C" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Schematic overview 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Real example 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-7A2C54A8-BDA6-408F-AD15-B9A44BC5017E" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6311AE69-8E80-4969-BBF4-49A9B07D5E8E-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6311AE69-8E80-4969-BBF4-49A9B07D5E8E-low.png"/></fig></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-3AFDE2F8-F649-453E-AC5F-9600B4E88D9A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-07E5C074-651E-4D6A-BD42-2C0FADF72F03-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-07E5C074-651E-4D6A-BD42-2C0FADF72F03-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-EC1EAE23-40EC-4B10-A2C9-83873F76DC70" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Collect</title><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Symptoms</b> 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Lines visible in carriage direction. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Length of the lines is in most cases equal to the width of the printed image. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> White and/or dark lines only visible in the 1st meter after the leading edge 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> After 1 meter the lines are no longer visible. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> White and/or dark lines are visible in all colors. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> The distance between the lines depends on the print mode. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-EE8066F2-86DB-4E1A-AA2D-D69BAF316027" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> Functional logging (if available)</b> </title><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Media step accuracy</i> 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The performance of the media on the platen is monitored in the graph “Media Step Accuracy”. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> In case an image is printed from the leading edge the media step controller has not yet started steering yet (the green line is at 0). 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">During this period the media steps (left and/or right side) might not be correct yet. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This can result in media step errors which can be visible (Orange and/or blue line are outside the green area). After 50-100 cm the green line shows steering behavior and the Orange and Blue lines move towards the green area. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> See example below. 
</p><fig id="GUID-D1559E96-8473-410F-9DAF-8ED75E742FE5" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-33890D82-CB52-4CD7-B3C9-C94FF3C2FE7E-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-33890D82-CB52-4CD7-B3C9-C94FF3C2FE7E-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-0286BFA2-BFD3-4DB7-ADCB-3C5D3BDBCBBD" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">ADAM-triggers</title><p class="- topic/p ">No ADAM triggers are available 
</p></section><section id="GUID-DDCC1BB0-B402-4010-9156-67DB737F3DE5" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Analyze/Repair</title><fig id="GUID-93BA1BC3-3AF0-4B47-B0AB-B528347BCFFA" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-1A966CC3-F9B9-43C6-AD00-420C8A708738-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-1A966CC3-F9B9-43C6-AD00-420C8A708738-svg.svg"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-BB9BDDD1-E29C-42C5-BF10-2854E3AE4223" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Steps explanation</title><table pgwide="1" id="GUID-D963269B-E108-446A-A212-4581FEAA8740" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="20*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col4" colnum="4" colwidth="30*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Type 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">To do 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check if the platen is polluted and/or the vacuum holes are blocked. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "/></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Perform maintenance 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Operating video : 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><xref href="http://localhost:20346/VIDEO10004EN.US/video06/index.html" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot usertext?>Clean the Platen</xref> 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> 
<xref href="http://localhost:20346/VIDEO10004EN.US/video19/index.html" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref "><?ditaot usertext?>Clean the Buffer Plate</xref> 
</p></li></ul></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Decision 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Check whether the media is calibrated 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">In case the media isn’t calibrated an exclamation sign is visible in the UI. 
</p><fig id="GUID-CBA39104-2BE0-4030-B562-51916E04A137" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-51A04FF7-0AFC-4927-984F-8E1D3D278823-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-51A04FF7-0AFC-4927-984F-8E1D3D278823-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">When the last calibration is done a long time ago calibrate the media again 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Cut media before calibration 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Perform media calibration including the leading edge 
</p></entry><entry colname="col4" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Cut media before calibration 
</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-2513E5DF-C282-453D-9841-6E539DB0EB51" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Evaluate/Prevention</title><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Calibrate the media on a regular basis. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Keep the platen and buffer plate clean. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-987F83F9-80F0-41BC-B82B-BB16DA268203" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Background info</title><p class="- topic/p ">The media step controller does not steer in the first 50 cm after the leading edge. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">During this timeframe the controller uses the latest calibration values without feedback-loop. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">When the calibration values are not correct white or dark lines can appear. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">When the controller starts steering the dark and/or white lines will disappear. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This artefact will not visible when the leading edge is not used (eg. Tight winding). 
</p></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-BDE42A10-0DAA-46D3-99F7-D18695E3843E.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Solutions</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
</task>